<table class="infobox" style="width:22em;width: 24em; background: #f2f9ff;"><tbody><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #99c2ff;">Zarathos</th></tr><tr><td colspan="2" style="text-align:center"><a href="/wiki/File:52_1_b-1-.jpg" class="image" title="Cover of Marvel Comics&#39; Ghost Rider #77"><img alt="Cover of Marvel Comics&#39; Ghost Rider #77" src="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/2/22/52_1_b-1-.jpg/240px-52_1_b-1-.jpg" decoding="async" width="240" height="368" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/2/22/52_1_b-1-.jpg 1.5x" data-file-width="261" data-file-height="400" /></a><div>Cover of Marvel Comics' <i><a href="/wiki/Ghost_Rider_(comic_book)" title="Ghost Rider (comic book)">Ghost Rider</a></i> #77</div></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background: #99c2ff;">Publication information</th></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;"><a href="/wiki/Category:Comics_publishing_companies" title="Category:Comics publishing companies">Publisher</a></th><td><a href="/wiki/Marvel_Comics" title="Marvel Comics">Marvel Comics</a></td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;"><a href="/wiki/First_appearance" title="First appearance">First appearance</a></th><td><i><a href="/wiki/Marvel_Spotlight" title="Marvel Spotlight">Marvel Spotlight</a></i> #5 (August 1972)</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;"><a href="/wiki/Category:Comics_creators" title="Category:Comics creators">Created by</a></th><td><a href="/wiki/Roy_Thomas" title="Roy Thomas">Roy Thomas</a>, <a href="/wiki/Gary_Friedrich" title="Gary Friedrich">Gary Friedrich</a>, and <a href="/wiki/Mike_Ploog" title="Mike Ploog">Mike Ploog</a></td></tr><tr><th colspan="2" style="text-align:center;background: #99c2ff;">In-story information</th></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Full name</th><td>Zarathos</td></tr><tr><th scope="row" style="width: 40%;">Species</th><td><a href="/wiki/List_of_Marvel_Comics_demons" title